  "description": "<b>根据《洛杉矶时报》的<a href=\"http://www.latimes.com/news/politics/la-pn-snowden-nsa-secrets-thumb-drive-20130613,0,791040.story\" target=\"_blank\">报道</a>，美国官员透露，<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2013/6/9/4412080/edward-snowden-comes-out-as-nsa-whistleblower-i-dont-want-to-live-in\" target=\"_blank\">NSA告密者Edward Snowden</a>之所以能够成功地从夏威夷的一处设施内<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2013/6/6/4403328/leaked-verizon-nsa-surveillance-court-order\" target=\"_blank\">带走机密文件</a>，是因为他违禁使用了一个\"拇指驱动器\"(U盘?)。</b>据称，调查人员有能力辨别出Snowden带走了哪些文件，并且是从哪些服务器上获得的。不过，其当前还没有公布Snowden是否拥有额外的文件。<br /><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d43db04/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241071.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0NSA%E5%91%8A%E5%AF%86%E8%80%85Edward+Snowden%E8%BF%9D%E8%A7%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8U%E7%9B%98%E5%B9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241071.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0NSA%E5%91%8A%E5%AF%86%E8%80%85Edward+Snowden%E8%BF%9D%E8%A7%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8U%E7%9B%98%E5%B9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241071.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0NSA%E5%91%8A%E5%AF%86%E8%80%85Edward+Snowden%E8%BF%9D%E8%A7%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8U%E7%9B%98%E5%B9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gp